{"tid":952769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國第二大電訊商O2無視國家封殺令，表示：華為合約都簽妥了呵呵！","createTime":"2018-12-23T11:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T00:26:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a03234d7b7ffe05cae879aa2d14d3f5800e4da","tid":952769,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181223/1338485.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181223%2F1338485.htm&d=NEW3CnzJChbXK%2BLXOUIjO%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=d6979a2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181223/1338485.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://applealmond.com/posts/45941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplealmond.com%2Fposts%2F45941&d=NEW3CnzJChbXK%2BLXOUIjO%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=9ff764c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://applealmond.com/posts/45941</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3784/3784276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3784%2F3784276.jpg&h=0f4ea5dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲英國第二大電信商O2將採用華為5G設備。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n英、美政府與情報機構日前以「國家安全」為由，要求國內電信商棄用華為5G技術與設備，但英國第二大電信商O2卻宣布，從2019年1月開始，將在倫敦200個基地台開始測試華為5G通訊系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，替換目前正在使用的NOKIA設備<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。O2發言人表示，「合約早就簽好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，表明華為在英國上路勢在必行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"6c9b67629482d8c98b758471e3c7c3f664eb5b83","tid":952769,"uid":10277,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"我華或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"4b282f60df1a8f141d7bf7d4ece7d6c74bff1bbb","tid":952769,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3727/3727914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3727%2F3727914.jpg&h=aea0c517&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n自2018年7月起，美國、澳洲、紐西蘭、英國、日本、法國等祭出「華為封殺令」，以「國家安全」為理由，要求禁用華為5G技術與設備。<br />\n<br />\n根據《金融時報》報導，這次O2公開宣布測試華為5G系統，意味著英國四大通訊商都已展開華為5G設備測試；另外三家供訊商包括市占率最大的EE，以及Vodafone和Three UK。<br />\n<br />\nEE作為英國電信集團（BT）旗下公司，自2018年2月起，就與華為展開一系列5G測試新空口（NR）的合作；Vodafone 2月也跟華為聯手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，在西班牙完成全球首個5G通話測試；Three UK則是與華為簽署價值20億英鎊（約778億新台幣）的網路架構合約。"},{"pid":"be99dd8ef6e7d9d1caaebd51f6f700b7eec281a7","tid":952769,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"雖然BT在12月5日宣布拒用華為核心5G網路設備，卻又承認華為的設備比NOKIA、愛立信（Ericsson）等競爭對手更為先進，最後以「公司內部政策」為理由，在5G核心技術上不採用華為設備。BT首席網路架構師尼爾&middot;麥克雷（Neil McRae）表示，「華為是目前唯一一家真正的5G供應商<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他公司還需要努力追趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n就連英國情報機構最高負責人軍情六處處長亞歷克斯&bull;揚格（Alex Younger）也承認，在5G技術上，英國是否使用華為面臨艱難抉擇，「5G技術基本上以中國技術，主要是華為技術為基礎。在我們的盟友立場明確的情況下，需要考慮我們是否會在（5G技術）平台的所有權問題上感到滿意，但這並不簡單。」<br />\n<br />\n現在O2消息一出，華為5G在國上路已成定局。華為公共及政府事務部19日曾指出，截止目前，華為已獲得25個5G商用合約，並與全球50多個商業夥伴簽署合作協議，5G基地台商用發貨數量也已超過1萬個，在業界遙遙領先。2019年上半年，華為將發布搭載5G芯片的5G智慧手機，並將在2019年下半年實現規模商用。"},{"pid":"7ee9c43f51b0aadd5ecb07a321f2f5bb19297cf2","tid":952769,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa8974e2168babfafb38ac606f3c4957602406b","tid":952769,"uid":213597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f29367e585014c4ec9657a765e8732d47be09cc","tid":952769,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f8c88ff9a2349adfede8fbcd088ca199ddf4db8","tid":952769,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"連燈hard brexitters幾時返去重建大英帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce9eeca3863915764d438c34887396df8d2f24f","tid":952769,"uid":38472,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"左膠抵死，等睇回歸中国。"},{"pid":"97c107ad8c2b7b70438d1fee5ece4bb24cd308fb","tid":952769,"uid":194281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"好快就會轉.美國佬仲唔搞死你"},{"pid":"aa359e0301f5282c7124f3ebb7a7cf2cf601da8a","tid":952769,"uid":20924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044089c11729b1325695b02ed1ebd77d611d9f2e","tid":952769,"uid":159159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"認真想問<br />\n其他公司真係未發展到5G咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f4cce4d039c0d1344ad57c26c085c38a1f6169","tid":952769,"uid":83623,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"依編文其實好怪, 睇O2 自己PR news 係同時同緊Nokia 合作緊，編文就講到個trial 好似得Huawei 咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.o2.co.uk/press-release/o2-launches-pilot-to-boost-london-network-ahead-of-5g/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.o2.co.uk%2Fpress-release%2Fo2-launches-pilot-to-boost-london-network-ahead-of-5g%2F&d=NEW3CnzJChbXK%2BLXOUIjO%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=09114a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.o2.co.uk/press-release/o2-launches-pilot-to-boost-london-network-ahead-of-5g/</a><br />\n仲有McRae 係係華為自己個論壇講, 更似Lip service多個BT現實情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lightreading.com/mobile/5g/bts-mcrae-huawei-is-the-only-true-5g-supplier-right-now/d/d-id/747734\